title: Colorado SOS, Registered voters by party affiliation by county, Colorado, Oct 2008
name: Colorado SOS, Registered voters by party affiliation by county, Colorado, Oct 2008
description:
The poly shapefile shows the number of registered voters by party affiliation and by county in Colorado. 
The data was downloaded from Colorado Secretary of State's (SOS) "Election Center" website and joined with the county shape file.

author.source: Colorado Secretary of State (SOS) Election Center website
